article.description: — Amari Williams scored 13 points as Drexel beat Fairfield 65-47 on Friday night.
article.headline: Williams puts up 13, Drexel beats Fairfield 65-47
article.linkText: Williams puts up 13, Drexel beats Fairfield 65-47
article.story: PHILADELPHIA -- — Amari Williams scored 13 points as Drexel beat Fairfield 65-47 on Friday night. Williams also added 13 rebounds for the Dragons (2-2). Jamie Bergens shot 4 for 9, including 2 for 5 from beyond the arc to add 10 points. Garfield Turner shot 4 of 4 from the field to finish with nine points. Brycen Goodine led the way for the Stags (1-3) with 15 points. Caleb Fields added 11 points, four assists and two steals for Fairfield. Peyton Smith also had 10 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
